Text: RENot a problem I understand completely Does your brother stand any chance of being deployed I hope not If you feel like getting dinner let me know Nick Original Message From Scott Susan M Sent Friday October PM To Stephan Nicholas J Subject RE sorry i didnt get back to you sooner this week about dinner but things have been crazy my brother and wife left yesterday to drive to kentucky and their new base so most of my free time was spent with family susan Original Message From Stephan Nicholas J Sent Tuesday October AM To Scott Susan M Subject Susan Do you feel like getting together for dinner this week to catch up Let me know when works for you Im fairly flexible this week Nick
